Package edu.purdue.cs59000.umltranslator.exceptions

  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    UMLSDInformationException
    UMLSDInformationException is a more specific Exception class than UMLSequenceDiagramException that identifies an issue with the information provided by the user sequence diagram.
    UMLSDStructureException
    UMLSDStructureException is a more specific Exception class than UMLSequenceDiagramException that identifies an issue with the structure of the Java representation of a sequence diagram.
    UMLSequenceDiagramException
    UMLSequenceDiagramException is an Exception class that identifies issues with either the generation of a Java representation of a user sequence diagram, a syntax error in the user sequence diagram, or an error in source code generation from a sequence diagram representation object.
